---
title: "create-api-contract — type → details → spec → diagram → stubs"
---
%%{init: {'theme': 'neutral'}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant Claude
    participant FS as File System

    User->>Claude: /create-api-contract [name] [--type <t>]

    note over Claude,User: Phase 1 — Protocol type
    alt type not given
        Claude->>User: [1] HTTP [2] GraphQL [3] WebSocket [4] Custom
        User-->>Claude: selection
    end

    note over Claude,User: Phase 2 — Contract details
    Claude->>User: Essential fields for <type>:<br/>(method+path / operation name / event name / protocol name)
    User-->>Claude: answers
    Claude->>User: Optional fields:<br/>(auth, errors, response shape)
    User-->>Claude: answers

    note over Claude: Phase 3 — Build spec
    Claude->>Claude: Render contract-<name>.md<br/>from collected fields

    note over Claude: Phase 4 — Build sequence diagram
    Claude->>Claude: Generate contract-<name>.mmd<br/>showing request round-trip

    note over Claude,User: Phase 5 — Preview + confirm
    Claude->>User: Preview of contract-<name>.md<br/>and contract-<name>.mmd<br/>[1] Accept [2] Edit details [3] Abort
    User-->>Claude: choice
    alt edit
        Claude->>User: Which field to change?
        User-->>Claude: correction
        Claude->>Claude: Re-render
        Claude->>User: Updated preview
        User-->>Claude: Accept
    end
    alt abort
        break Skill aborts
            Claude->>User: Aborted, no files written
        end
    end

    note over Claude,FS: Write artefacts
    Claude->>FS: Write .claude/docs/contract-<name>.md
    FS-->>Claude: OK
    Claude->>FS: Write .claude/sequences/contract-<name>.mmd
    FS-->>Claude: OK

    note over Claude,User: Phase 6 — Optional stubs
    Claude->>User: Generate code stubs?<br/>[1] Backend + frontend [2] Backend only<br/>[3] Frontend only [4] Skip
    User-->>Claude: choice
    opt stubs requested
        Claude->>User: Stubs printed in chat<br/>(not written to source files)
    end

    Claude->>User: Contract created:<br/>.claude/docs/contract-<name>.md<br/>.claude/sequences/contract-<name>.mmd<br/>Next: /analyze-api-contracts to verify implementation matches spec
